Privacy Policy for Hasch-Klastch

This app does not collect any personally identifiable information from you. We respect your privacy, and your privacy is important to us.

Data Storage

Local Highscore: The app stores your highscore locally to track your personal performance within the app. This data is exclusively stored on your device and is not collected or transmitted by us. You cannot manually remove this data from the app; it will only be deleted if you uninstall the app from your device.

Advertising

This app may display ads through Google AdMob. Please note that Google AdMob may collect anonymous device information and usage data to display relevant ads. For more information on Google AdMob's privacy policy, please refer to https://policies.google.com/privacy?hl=de.

Changes to this Privacy Policy

We reserve the right to change this privacy policy at any time. Changes will be posted within the app, and the date at the beginning of this statement will indicate when the policy was last updated.

Contact

If you have any questions or concerns regarding your privacy concerning this app, you can contact us at kai.development@gmail.com.
